	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Today, the doctor comes in and gives me a smile. He seems excited, but not very. It's like he is trying to make an effort to be happy on my behalf."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "My parents are here. It's been a few days since I've last seen them. Both of them are even sort of dressed up. Is this supposed to be some kind of special occasion? It's not a party."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "There is this ritual the head cardiologist has. He takes his time, sorting his papers, then setting them aside as if to make a point of the pointlessness of what he just did."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Then he casually sits down on the edge of the bed next to mine. He looks me in the eyes for a moment."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Hello, Hisao. How are you today?"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I don't answer him but I smile a little, back at him."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I believe that you can go home; your heart is stronger now, and with some precautions, you should be fine."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "We have all your medication sorted out. I'll give your father the prescription."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "The doctor hands a sheet of paper to my dad, whose expression turns wooden as he reads it quickly."),
	Line.new("Dad", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "So many…"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I take it from his hand and take a look myself, feeling numb. How am I supposed to react to this?"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.ACTIVEBACKGROUND = LOADEDBACKGROUNDS["white"];March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "The absurdly long list of medications staring back at me from the paper seems insurmountable. They all blend together in a sea of letters."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "This is insane."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Side effects, adverse effects, contraindications and dosages are listed line after line with cold precision."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I try to read them, but it's so futile."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I can't understand any of it. Attempting to only makes me feel sicker."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "All this… for the rest of my life, every day?"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.ACTIVEBACKGROUND = LOADEDBACKGROUNDS["hosp_room"];March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I'm afraid that is the best we can do at this point."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "However, new medications are always being developed, so I wouldn't be surprised to see that list fade over the years."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Years… What kind of confidence booster is that? I'd have felt better if he hadn't said anything at all…"),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Also, I've spoken with your parents and we believe that it would be best if you don't return to your old school."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "What!?"),
	Line.new("Dad", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Please, calm down, Hisao. Listen to what the doctor has to say…"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Calm down? The way he says it tells me he knew full well that I wouldn't like it. Am I going to be home schooled?"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Whatever of my concern shows, it's ignored."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "We all understand that your education is paramount; however, I don't think that it's wise for you to be without supervision."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "At least not until we're sure that your medication is suitable."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "So, I've spoken to your parents about a transfer."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It's a school called Yamaku Academy that specializes in dealing with disabled students."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Disabled? What? Am I…"),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It has a 24-hour nursing staff and it's only a few minutes from a highly regarded general hospital. The majority of students live on the campus."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Think of it as a boarding school of sorts. It's designed to give students a degree of independence, while keeping help nearby."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Independence? It's a school for disabled kids. Don't try to disguise that fact."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "If it was really that “free,” there wouldn't be a 24-hour nursing staff, and you wouldn't make a hospital being nearby a selling point."),
	Line.new("Dad", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Of course, that's only if you want to go. But… your mother and I aren't really able to home school you."),
	Line.new("Dad", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "We went out there and had a look a couple of weeks back; I think you'd like it."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It looks like I really don't have a choice."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Compared to other heart problems, people with your condition usually tend to live long lives. You'll need a job one day and this is a good opportunity to continue your education."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "This isn't an opportunity, don't call it an opportunity. Don't call it a goddamned opportunity."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Well, you should be excited at the chance to go back to school. I remember you wanted to return to school, and while it's not the same one…"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "A special school. That's…"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "An insult. That is what I want to say. It's a step down."),
	Line.new("Dad", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It's not what you think. All of the students there are pretty active, in their own sort of way."),
	Line.new("Dad", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It's geared towards students that can still get around and learn, but just need a little help… in one way or another."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Your father's right. And many of the graduates of the school have gone on to do amazing things. A person doesn't have to be held back by their disability."),
	Line.new("Doctor", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "One of my colleagues in another hospital is a graduate."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I don't care. A person doesn't have to be held back by their disability? That's what a disability is."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I really hate that something so important was decided for me. But what can I do about it? A “normal” life is out of the question now."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It's funny, I had always thought my life was actually kind of boring, but now I miss it."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I want to protest. I want to blame this lack of reaction on shock, or fatigue. I could easily yell out something now - something about how I can go back to school anyway. But, no."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I don't say anything. The fact is that I know now it's futile."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I look around the room, feeling very tired of all this. The hospital, doctors, my condition, everything. I don't see anything that would make me feel any different."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "There really isn't a choice. I know this, but the thought of going to a disabled school… what are those even like? As much as I try to put a positive spin on this, it's very difficult."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "But let me try."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "A clean slate isn't a bad thing."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "That is all I can think of to get me through this. At least I still have something; even if it's a “special school,” it's something. It's a fresh start, and my life isn't over. It would be a mistake to just resign myself to thinking that."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "At the very least, I'll try to see what my new life will look like."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.ACTIVEBACKGROUND = LOADEDBACKGROUNDS["school_gate"];March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "The gate looked far too pompous for what it was."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "In fact, gates in general seem to do that, but this one especially so."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Red bricks, black wrought iron and gray plaster, assembled into a whole that didn't feel welcoming at all."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I wondered if it looked like what a gate for a school should look like, but couldn't really decide. Probably no."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Of course I didn't want to get stuck on thinking about the gate for too long, so I entered through it with a brisk pace that felt surprisingly good."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Moving forward feels good."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.ACTIVEBACKGROUND = LOADEDBACKGROUNDS["school_courtyard"];March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "So I walk towards the main building of Yamaku Academy with this brisk pace. I'm alone, as my parents are taking my stuff to the dorms, and there's supposed to be someone waiting for me."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "The grounds are incredibly lush, filled with green."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It doesn't feel like the kind of grounds a school would have, more like a park, with a clean walkway going past trees and the smell of fresh-cut grass and all other park-like things."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Words like “clean” and “hygienic” pop into my mind. It makes me shudder."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I shake them off. Stay open-minded now. It's your new life. You have to take it as it comes."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "That's what I tell myself."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "A few big buildings loom behind the leafy canopies, too big and too many for just a school."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Everything seems off; it's different from what I thought I knew about schools."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It's an uncanny valley. Even though I was told this is my new school, in the back of my head it doesn't feel like one."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I wonder if the feeling is real or caused by my expectations of a school for the disabled."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Speaking of that, I don't see anyone else here. It's kinda eerie."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It makes me wish there was somebody here so I could anchor myself to something tangible instead of having this feeling that I stepped into another dimension."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "The trees hum with the wind and the green hues flashing all around me catch my attention."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It makes me think about hospitals again, how they say that the operating rooms are painted green because green is a calming color."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "So why am I feeling so anxious, despite all this greenery?"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "…"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Only after I stand in front of the haughty main building, I surprise myself by realizing why the gate bothered me:"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It was the last chance I had to turn back, even if I had no life I could return to."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "But still, after entering, there was absolutely no way I could go back any more."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Feeling nervous and with this realization set in my head, I open the front door."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.ACTIVEBACKGROUND = LOADEDBACKGROUNDS["school_lobby"];March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "A tall man with bad posture notices me as I enter. We're the only people in the lobby, so it's only logical."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("???", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "You must be… Ni… Na… Niki?"),
	Line.new("Hisao", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Nakai."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("???", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "So you are. Excellent. I'm your homeroom and science teacher. My name is Mutou."),
	Line.new("Mutou", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Welcome."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "We exchange a handshake that is neither firm nor sloppy, and he looks at his watch."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("Mutou", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "The head nurse asked you for a brief check-in visit, but there's no time for that now."),
	Line.new("Hisao", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Oh. Should I go later?"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("Mutou", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Yes, afternoon is probably fine. We should get going and introduce you to the rest of the class. They're waiting already."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Waiting for me? I don't really like being the center of attention, but I guess it's inevitable in a situation like this."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Somehow, not knowing what is waiting for me makes me feel really nervous."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Thinking of this, I almost miss what the teacher is saying."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("Hisao", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Why? Do I have to?"),
	Line.new("Mutou", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Of course not. That's why I asked."),
	Line.new("Hisao", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Right."),
	Line.new("Mutou", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Let's go then."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("Hisao", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Yeah, sure. I mean, isn't that normal?"),
	Line.new("Mutou", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Of course. But not everyone likes to be at the center of attention."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I'm probably one of those people, but I guess I should be the one to give the first impression of myself."),
	Line.new("Hisao", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Right, but it's no problem."),
	Line.new("Mutou", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Let's go then."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.ACTIVEBACKGROUND = LOADEDBACKGROUNDS["school_staircase2"];March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "My heart is pounding in my chest and it keeps me thinking about my condition as I follow the teacher up the stairs."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.ACTIVEBACKGROUND = LOADEDBACKGROUNDS["school_hallway3"];March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "The third door down the third floor corridor is marked as the classroom for class 3-3."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() Sound.play(LOADEDSFX["sfx_dooropen"], NO_LOOP);March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Mutou opens the door and enters."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("Mutou", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Good morning everyone, sorry I'm late again."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I hesitate for a split second at the door, freezing on the spot."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.ACTIVEBACKGROUND = LOADEDBACKGROUNDS["school_hallway3"];March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Ah, get a grip! This is a big step, I know that… But there isn't any point to worrying so much about it, at least not this soon."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.ACTIVEBACKGROUND = LOADEDBACKGROUNDS["hisao_class_start"];March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I follow the teacher into the classroom and look around, partially so I won't have to meet the curious gazes of my new classmates."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "It's pretty spacious; the ceiling is unusually high and there's lots of space left over around and inbetween the desks."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "An entire wall taken up by blackboards and the high, old fashioned windows only make it seem larger."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "The students' desks are just standard wooden desks with a shelf underneath for books and wooden chairs with metal frames. Simple and efficient."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I stop walking in front of the classroom and face the other students. They all look normal, like students in any other school. But then, why would they be here?"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.ACTIVEBACKGROUND = LOADEDBACKGROUNDS["hisao_class_move"];March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "They're probably like me and have something wrong with them, only it's just not immediately obvious. Then, I notice that one of the girls seems to be missing the thumb of her right hand. It's a little jarring."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Despite the natural tendency to listen when someone's talking about you, I tune out the teacher's speech halfway through while he introduces me to the class."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I notice a flash of dark hair and see that someone is looking at me. A girl with really long, straight hair that is pretty eye-catching. As she sees me looking back at her, she covers her face with her hands as if it will make her invisible."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "There is one boy with a cane leaning against the lockers at the rear of the class. It's weird seeing someone so young with a cane."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Another girl seems to be making some weird hand motions. Sign language? She peers at me over the rims of her glasses, then goes back to whatever she's doing."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "She's kind of cute. So is the cheery-looking girl with pink hair sitting next to her. She's really hard to miss; I don't know how I didn't notice her the moment I walked in…"),
	Line.new("Mutou", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "…please welcome our newest classmate."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "He claps his hands and so does everyone else, except one girl in the first row who has only one hand. I cringe a little, but hide it by bowing in thanks for this applause I did not deserve."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "After the applause, there is a brief silence that nobody seems to want to be responsible for breaking."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "The teacher soon realizes that he should probably say something. He opens up with some unintelligible noise, shuts up as he loses his momentum, and then starts introducing me."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Nobody seems to be too interested."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Maybe I should've said yes to the self-introduction thing."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Probably realizing he doesn't know anything about me, he just ends up saying my name wrong again, and asks me to write it on the blackboard."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I do that, and turn back to face the class, feeling awkward."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "", function() March22.NextLine(); end ),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "A collective silence tells me that I should open my mouth now."),
	Line.new("Hisao", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "So… I'm Hisao Nakai."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "And after that?"),
	Line.new("Hisao", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "My hobbies are reading and soccer. I hope to get along well with everyone even though I'm a new student."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "And after that?"),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I'm being so boring. This is exactly like every self-introduction ever. I should say something more. Something more exciting."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "I end up saying nothing, and the teacher picks up from there."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "Everyone seems to be satisfied even with what little I said, though. A few girls are whispering to each other, throwing glances at me. It could've gone worse."),
	Line.new("", Color.new(255, 255, 255), "…"),
